edu.uidaho.junicon.substrates.groovy.iterators

Class IconVariadicFunction<T,R>

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.uidaho.junicon.substrates.groovy.iterators.IconVariadicFunction<T,R>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    VariadicFunction<T,R>

    public class IconVariadicFunction<T,R>
extends Object
implements VariadicFunction<T,R>
    Converts Groovy closures to Java lambda expressions, using VariadicFunction. Wraps Groovy Closure as VariadicFunction that delegates to it. For use by unpackArgs() in IconIterator.
